OL,3,CMore than 150 people contact police in
OL,4,Cprobe into ex-neurologist
OL,6,FMore than 150 people have contacted
OL,7,Fdetectives carrying out an
OL,8,Finvestigation into the clinical
OL,9,Fpractices of former consultant
OL,10,Fneurologist Dr Michael Watt.
OL,12,FProviding an update on Operation
OL,13,FBegrain, police have made a new appeal
OL,14,Ffor former patients of the doctor who
OL,15,Fwas at the centre of Northern
OL,16,FIreland's largest recall of patients
OL,17,Fto come forward.
