OL,3,CMore than 150 people contact police in
OL,4,Cprobe into ex-neurologist
OL,6,FIn 2018, more than 4,000 of Dr Watt's
OL,7,Fpatients attended recall appointments
OL,8,Famid concerns over his clinical
OL,9,Fpractice.
OL,11,FLast year, he was struck off the
OL,12,Fmedical register after a tribunal
OL,13,Ffound his fitness to practise was
OL,14,Fcurrently impaired and that his
OL,15,Fprofessional performance was
OL,16,Funacceptable.
OL,18,FPolice then launched the probe into
OL,19,Fhis work.
