OL,6,FDetective Inspector Gina Quinn said:
OL,7,F"Michael Watt worked for the Belfast
OL,8,FHealth and Social Care Trust, and also
OL,9,Fheld private clinics at Hillsborough
OL,10,FPrivate Clinic and the Ulster
OL,11,FIndependent Clinic.
OL,13,F"Last November, we launched an
OL,14,Finvestigation into the former
OL,15,Fconsultant neurologist's clinical
OL,16,Fpractices.
