OL,6,F"We highlighted how former patients,
OL,7,For their next of kin or
OL,8,Frepresentatives, could report any
OL,9,Fconcerns regarding their medical
OL,10,Ftreatment to police.
OL,12,F"Since that time, 154 people have
OL,13,Fcontacted our Operation Begrain
OL,14,Finvestigation team."
OL,16,FShe added: "We continue to encourage
OL,17,Fanyone with concerns to use the online
OL,18,Freporting form where possible.
