OL,6,F"It will guide you through the
OL,7,Fquestions, and is available 24 hours a
OL,8,Fday. It's the quickest and easiest way
OL,9,Fto make a report.
OL,11,F"However, anyone unable to use the
OL,12,Fonline reporting facility can make a
OL,13,Fphone call.
OL,15,F"The new number to call is 028 3025
OL,16,F9200, and a voicemail facility is in
OL,17,Fplace. Simply leave your contact
OL,18,Fdetails and a member of the team will
OL,19,Fget back to you.
